WEBVTT

00:00,000 --> 00:04,950
When most output rises but outcomes stay flat, decision rhythm is usually the bottleneck.

00:05,000 --> 00:09,950
Teams often move faster on content than on gamification clarity in weekly operations.

00:10,000 --> 00:14,950
Assign one owner, track one metric, and review one live decision every week.

00:15,000 --> 00:19,950
Run a one-week pilot, capture evidence from real behavior, then adjust immediately.

00:20,000 --> 00:24,950
That pattern raises first-pass quality, strengthens weekly review quality, and reduces avoidable rework.

00:25,000 --> 00:29,950
What is one decision checkpoint you can run this week?
